{
  "stem": "6803.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then there was an order that we're not allowed to leave the barracks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If we have to go to the bathroom in the middle of the night, only naked.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If you're naked, then they wouldn't shoot you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If you have a little clothes, they were thinking that the partisans coming in or something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they didn't want-- you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they told us to go to the bathroom naked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So this was the sign that we are inmates from the camp, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, um, we stood there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We stayed there for about three months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they got together, got us together in the Appellplatz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they told us we're gonna leave this camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we stood in Appell for about three, four hours in middle of the day.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or I think till the evening, till it got dark.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then I remember to go, where we stood there in line, to get up to the train was a little hill-- a little-- a little hill to go up there.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was, you know, not a straight-- a straight running.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was dark.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't see.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And both sides, there were Germans, SS, with the sticks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And beating us, no matter where.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "People were felling down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were running.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We didn't know where to run.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We didn't know where we're gonna run.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In the meantime, they beat us with a stick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Lucky me, I-- I-- I hid myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I didn't get hit, not once even.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I fell down, and I got up, and I run right away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We got into the, uh, to the-- to the-- to the cattle wagon, there like you call it.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
